reference "sec:Results"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

 details the multi-faceted feature choice strategy and the composite scoring system used to determine the best biomarkers.
 Finally,
 Section 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec:Conclusions"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

 discusses implications of the research results,
 points out limitations of the study,
 and suggests directions of future research.
\end_layout

